      <p
        begin="02:22:52.906"
        end="02:22:55.075"><span region="Default">♪ Awak tahu cara bermain<br/>Saya tahu Aristotle ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:22:55.701"
        end="02:22:58.370"><span region="Default">♪ Serba baharu, pecutan penuh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:22:58.453"
        end="02:23:01.123"><span region="Default">♪ Sentuh saya sementara kawan awak<br/>main Grand Theft Auto ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:23:01.206"
