      <p
        begin="02:47:23.168"
        end="02:47:25.087"><span region="Default">♪ Aku akan silap ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:47:25.170"
        end="02:47:28.423"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, tetapi hidup diteruskan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:47:28.507"
