        end="03:11:21.940"><span region="Default">Bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:26.945"
        end="03:11:29.406"><span region="Default">♪ Air mata nilam di muka saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:29.489"
        end="03:11:32.701"><span region="Default">♪ Kesedihan menjadi seluruh langit saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:32.784"
        end="03:11:35.787"><span region="Default">♪ Tapi ada lelaki kata aura saya batu bulan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:35.871"
        end="03:11:39.208"><span region="Default">♪ Hanya sebab dia khayal ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:39.291"
        end="03:11:40.667"><span region="Default">♪ Dan kita menari sepanjang malam ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:40.751"
        end="03:11:43.378"><span region="Default">♪ Dan awak boleh cuba ubah fikiran saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:43.462"
        end="03:11:45.047"><span region="Default">♪ Tapi awak mungkin kena beratur ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:45.714"
        end="03:11:47.424"><span region="Default">♪ Apa yang seorang gadis boleh buat? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:47.508"
        end="03:11:50.219"><span region="Default">♪ Berlian memang harus bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:50.302"
        end="03:11:52.429"><span region="Default">♪ Percayalah, aku masih berhias permata ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:11:52.513"
